  <h3>Financial Aid</h3>
  <p>Need-based financial aid is available. You may apply for need-based financial aid during the digital registration process, with the opportunity to apply for a 25% or 50% reduction in cost.</p>
  
  <h2>Sign Up</h2>
  <p>Ready to become a Brandeis Sports Center member? Great! <br>
    To sign up, simply fill out the form below with your name, email, and preferred membership type. Don't miss out on the opportunity to join our vibrant community of sports and fitness enthusiasts!"</p>
  <form action="/membership/signup" method="POST">
    <label for="name">Name:</label>
    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required><br>
    
    <label for="email">Email:</label>
    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required><br>
    
    <label for="membershipType">Membership Type:</label>
    <select id="membershipType" name="membershipType" required>
      <option value="">Choose a membership type</option>
      <option value="annualComprehensive">Annual Comprehensive</option>
      <option value="annualLectureActivities">Annual Lecture & Activities</option>
      <option value="seasonalComprehensive">Seasonal Comprehensive</option>
      <option value="seasonalLectureActivities">Seasonal Lecture & Activities</option>
    </select><br>

    <input type="submit" value="Submit">
</form>

   
